Sentencas: One dimensional (1-D) Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-delta (SYCO) nanofibers and nanofiber-based Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-delta-Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SYCO-GDC) composites have been prepared and studied as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: One-dimensional Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-δ nanofibers as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: 1-D SYCO nanofibers are synthesized by electrospinning technique and the subsequent calcination processes.
Titulo: One-dimensional Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-δ nanofibers as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction (XRD) results indicate that 900 degrees C is adequate for the formation of phase pure SYCO, much lower than the temperatures adopted in other reported methods for SYCO synthesis.
Titulo: One-dimensional Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-δ nanofibers as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: 1-D nanofiber-based SYCO-GDC composite cathodes have been fabricated by infiltrating the ionic conducting GDC phase into the porous SYCO nanofiber scaffolds, achieving interfacial polarization resistances of 0.651, 0.200, 0.057 and 0.011 Omega cm(2) at 600, 650, 700 and 750 degrees C, respectively, with an optimized SYCO:GDC mass ratio of 1:0.44.
Titulo: One-dimensional Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-δ nanofibers as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The stability of this SYCO-GDC (1:0.44) composite cathode was affirmed by 108-h constant current test.
Titulo: One-dimensional Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-δ nanofibers as cathode material for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: All these results suggest that 1-D nanofiber-based SYCO-GDC composite is a promising cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: One-dimensional Sr0.7Y0.3CoO2.65-δ nanofibers as cathode material for IT-SOFCs
